**Best budget solitaire:** [Knife Edge 14K WG at $925](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/knife-edge-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-316048?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (981 reviews). Save $75 versus the Petite Solitaire and redirect it toward diamond quality. 981 reviews provides strong independent validation.

**Best for maximum apparent size:** [Falling Edge Pavé Halo 14K WG at $2,410](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/falling-edge-pave-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-311113?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (368 reviews) + [2ct G-VS2 at $17,480](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-search?Shape=Oval&Carats=2&Color=G&Clarity=VS2&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = **[$19,890](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings?MetalType=wg&ShapeID=Oval&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**. Halo adds 20–30% face-up size; the white gold frame reads as contemporary high-contrast sparkle.

**Best lab-grown white gold oval:** [Petite Solitaire 14K WG at $1,000](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/petite-solitaire-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-item-194386?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (1,020 reviews) + [2ct IGI G-VVS2 lab at $2,847](https://www.bluenile.com/lab-grown-diamond-search?Shape=Oval&Carats=2&Color=G&Clarity=VVS2&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) = **[$3,847](https://www.bluenile.com/lab-grown-diamond-search?Shape=Oval&Carats=2&a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational)**. A 2ct oval in the most reviewed white gold setting for under $4,000.

**Best pavé band:** [Riviera Pavé Diamond 14K WG at $1,515](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/riviera-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-1-6-ct-tw-item-195326?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (390 reviews). The most validated full-pavé white gold band — 1/6 ct total weight in a full riviera pattern.

**Best three-stone white gold oval:** [Marquise Three Stone at $1,970](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/marquise-cut-diamond-three-stone-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315103?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) (152 reviews). Marquise wings create the same elongation effect as the oval center stone — the two shapes compound each other's finger-lengthening effect in white gold.

